snippet.title: Disney Infinity 2.0 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Disney Infinity: Marvel Super Heroes (2.0 Edition) has been announced for the PS4, PS3, Xbox One, Xbox 360, Nintendo Wii U, PC, and iOS tablets and smart phones.

Follow Disney Infinity 2.0 at GameSpot.com!
http://www.gamespot.com/disney-infinity-20/

Check out our review!
